    "# Calculate percentiles\n",
    "visibility_25th = data['Visibility_km'].quantile(0.25)\n",
    "pressure_75th = data['Press_kPa'].quantile(0.75)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Filter based on conditions\n",
    "advanced_filter = data[\n",
    "    (data['Visibility_km'] < visibility_25th) & \n",
    "    (data['Press_kPa'] > pressure_75th) & \n",
    "    (data['Weather'].str.contains('Rain|Snow', case=False, na=False))\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "# Frequency and average calculations\n",
    "frequency = advanced_filter.shape[0]\n",
    "avg_wind_speed = advanced_filter['Wind Speed_km/h'].mean()\n",
    "avg_humidity = advanced_filter[''].mean()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Number of instances:\", frequency)\n",
    "print(\"Average Wind Speed:\", avg_wind_speed)\n",
    "print(\"Average Relative Humidity:\", avg_humidity)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Display the filtered records\n",
    "print(advanced_filter)\n"
   ]
